        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nYep, \nYou must not +2/+1/merge alone - technically speaking it must even not be allowed - I will contact LF to see why you had this super power here.\n\nThe verification +1 is given by a verification job, so wait for its processing. We can help to fix the errors if needed. (Bartek will publish a ptach to fix the trivial error in json) In Open Source communities, reviewing is key as it is the engine of the collective intelligence.\nThere is no strict rules, but for integration I would like to see at least 2x +2 (not only the author) or 1x+2 and more than 2x+1.\nNo rush to publish..",
